```
$route[&#39;default_controller&#39;] = &#39;1st_Controller&#39;;
$route[&#39;404_override&#39;] = &#39;&#39;;
$route[&#39;translate_uri_dashes&#39;] = FALSE;
$route[&#39;2nd_Controller&#39;] = &#39;2nd_Controller&#39;;

```

Now everything is working perfectly. Thanks for all the help

